data.description: LOCATION!!! LOCATION!!! LOCATION!!! This beautiful 3 bedroom/2 bath home sits on 2.34 acres located in the fast-growing Golden Gate Estates area close to the Publix shopping center and Restaurants. It features lots of upgrades throughout the home including cathedral ceilings, granite countertops in the kitchen, stainless steel appliances, double sink vanity in the master bathroom, and a 300-gallon reverse osmosis system. HORSES OK!!! There is more than enough room for a pool or barn.  This will be a great property for a family because of its excellent location. Don't miss this opportunity to enjoy the COUNTRY LIFE and own a slice of paradise in Naples, FL!!!
